room_title: Escape room "8th Horcrux" by Great Escape of Central Texas in Killeen
room_address: 4400 E. Central Texas Expy Killeen, TX 76543
room_description: The story of the boy who lived… isn’t over yet. Was “He Who Must Not Be Named” really defeated? Wormtail kept a piece of Lord Voldemort's soul and hid it deep inside the castle. You and your team of students are on a quest to discover the secret passage to the 8th Horcrux to truly defeat the dark lord.
